<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>네이버::페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다.</title>
    <style>
        /* reset */
        html, body{height: 100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust: none;}
        html,body,div,dl,dt,dd,ul,ol,li,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6,p,table,th,td,form,fieldset,legend,textarea,input,select,textarea,button,figure,figcaption,a,span,address,strong {margin: 0;padding: 0;box-sizing: border-box;-webkit-box-sizing: border-box;}
        body,input,select,textarea,button,h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6,a{color: #000;font-family:'NanumSquare','나눔스퀘어',AppleSDGothicNeo-Regular,"Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;	font-size: 12px;font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2; -webkit-appearance: none;appearance: none;}
        img {border: 0;vertical-align: top;}
        ul,ol,li{list-style: none;}
        em,address{font-style: normal;}
        a{color: inherit;text-decoration: none;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;}
        a:hover,a:active,a:focus{text-decoration: none;outline: 0;}
        table{border-collapse: collapse;border-spacing: 0;}
        button{border: none;background: none;cursor: pointer;-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;}
        .blind{overflow: hidden;position: absolute !important;width: 1px;height: 1px;border: 0;padding: 0;clip: rect(0px, 0px, 0px, 0px);}


        /* style */
        .wrap{min-width: 1200px;}
        .wrap .inner{max-width:1100px; margin: 0 auto;text-align: center;}
        .header .inner{padding: 76px 0 0;}
        .header .logo_link{display: block;margin-left:40px;width:90px;height:18px;background: url(https://hangeul.pstatic.net/hangeul_static/errors/logo_pc_v2.png) no-repeat 0 0;background-size: 90px 18px;}
        .container .inner{padding: 139px 0 50px;}
        .container .ct_title{margin-bottom:22px;font-size: 40px;font-weight:900;letter-spacing: -2.4px;color: #111;}
        .container .text_green{color: #03c75a;}
        .container .desc_text{margin-bottom:45px;font-size: 24px; line-height: 36px; letter-spacing: -1.44px; color: #939393;}
        .container .btn_area{margin-bottom:182px;font-size: 0;}
        .container .btn_area a[class^="btn_"]{display: inline-block;vertical-align:top;width:160px;font-size: 24px;line-height: 58px;letter-spacing: -1.44px;color: #424242;border: 1px solid #e3e7e8;background-color: #fafbfc;}
        .container .btn_home{margin-left: 10px;} 
        .footer .inner{padding: 20px 0 130px;border-top: 1px solid #ddd;}
        .footer .footer_copy{font-size: 12px;line-height: 46px;letter-spacing: -0.72px;color: #b0b0b0;}
    </style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="wrap">
    <header class="header">
        <div class="inner">
            <h1 class="logo">
                <a href="https://naver.com/" class="logo_link">
                    <span class="blind">NAVER</span>
                </a>
            </h1>
        </div>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="inner">
            <h2 class="ct_title">
                혹시, <span class="text_green">잘못된 주소</span>가 아닌가요?
            </h2>
            <p class="desc_text">
                페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다. 잘못된 주소가 아니라면,<br>
                페이지가 삭제되었거나 주소가 변경되었을 수 있습니다.<br>
                다시 한번 확인해 주시기 바랍니다.
            </p>
            <div class="btn_area">
                <a class="btn_prev" href="javascript:history.back()">이전 페이지</a>
                <a class="btn_home" href="https://naver.com/">네이버 홈</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="inner">
            <a href="https://www.navercorp.com/" class="footer_copy">
                Copyright © NAVER Corp. All Rights Reserved.
            </a>
        </div>
    </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>

